## Description {#details}

RuntimeDyldMachOTarget - Templated base class for generic <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/macho">MachO</a> linker algorithms and data structures.

Concrete, target specific sub-classes can be accessed via the <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/scalar/placesafepoints-cpp/#abd1ccb1bf511e1965414eb1d2e137302">impl()</a> methods. (i.e. the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/runtimedyldmacho">RuntimeDyldMachO</a> hierarchy uses the Curiously Recurring Template Idiom). Concrete subclasses for each target can be found in ./Targets.

Definition at line 140 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/executionengine/lib/executionengine/runtimedyld/runtimedyldmacho-h">RuntimeDyldMachO.h</a>.
